  "scientificAccuracy": "This flowchart is based on comprehensive biochemical characterization of E. coli glycolytic enzymes. All enzymes, intermediates, cofactors, regulatory mechanisms, and alternative pathways have been extensively validated. The model represents the canonical glycolytic pathway with bacterial-specific features.",
